block content
  h1= title
  h2 Usage
  h3 Image search endpoint
    code  #{host}/api/imagesearch/<search teram>?offset=x
  p This will return an array of search results paginated to x. Each result will contain the URL of the image along with some  metadata of the image.
  h3 Latest image search endpoint
    code  #{host}/api/latest/imagesearch
  p This will return an array of searches made so far. If no search has been made and you are calling this endpoint, then you will get this output
    code  {status: 'No search made'}
  blockquote
    strong
      a(href="https://www.freecodecamp.com/challenges/image-search-abstraction-layer", target="_blank") https://www.freecodecamp.com/challenges/image-search-abstraction-layer
